      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine is currently unreliable and requires extensive mechanical work to be roadworthy, while the transmission suffers from significant slipping and delayed engagement. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches and dented panels, and the interior cabin has substantial tearing and staining throughout. Please expect to tow this vehicle as it is not currently fit for regular daily use.",
