      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a quality car that's ready to hit the road today. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and drives like a dream. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
