      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically sorted, featuring documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural integrity under lateral load. The dual-VANOS system has been recalibrated for optimal valve timing, ensuring a linear torque curve up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and an upgraded cooling system, this chassis delivers exceptional feedback and turn-in response. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the powertrain and drivetrain remain robust, making this an ideal candidate for the purist enthusiast.",
